<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1245610-is-this-anything-like-gone-girl-or-girl">Is this anything like &quot;Gone Girl&quot; or &quot;Girl on a Train&quot;? I hated both of those books and now I consider anything in the &quot;Suspense/Thriller&quot; genre to be suspect.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1245610'><a id="like_count_community_question_1245610" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1245610?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">166 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F34848682-the-woman-in-the-window">like</a></span>

