<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_28187230'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28187230-the-woman-in-cabin-10"><img alt="The Woman in Cabin 10" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1465878007l/28187230._SX98_.jpg" />
