      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/7992137.A_J_Finn">About A.J. Finn</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/7992137.A_J_Finn"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1513715025p3/7992137.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/7992137.A_J_Finn">A.J. Finn
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
6,006
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5265140640713337170">A.J. Finn, pseudonym for Daniel Mallory, has written for numerous publications, including the <i>Los Angeles Times</i>, the <i>Washington Post</i>, and the <i>Times Literary Supplement</i> (UK). A native of New York, Finn lived in England for ten years as a book editor before returning to New York City.</span>

</div>
</div>

